Material Information Summary - Anson Resources (ASX: ASN)

Key Highlights:

  • Higher Lithium Grades: Recent swabbing assays average 135 mg/l Li, 44% higher than the initial JORC resource estimate (93.5 mg/l).
  • Resource Upgrade Confirmed: Higher grades will be incorporated into a future JORC Mineral Resource upgrade.
  • Clean Brine Advantage: Low contaminants (e.g., Mg, Ca, B) compared to peers (Standard Lithium, Salton Sea), reducing processing costs.
  • Operational Efficiency: Higher lithium concentration may lower OPEX by reducing brine throughput and disposal requirements.
  • Next Steps:
  • Re-entry of Mt Fuel-Skyline Geyser well (approved by regulators) to expand resource.
  • Flow/pump tests to assess aquifer properties.
  • Targeting porous zones near the Ten Mile Graben, a potential lithium brine pathway.

Market Implications:

  • Positive for resource scalability and project economics.
  • Confirms technical viability of the DLE process (98% Li recovery, 99% impurity rejection).

Material Information Summary

Strategic Partnership & Technology Breakthrough

  • MOU signed with MTM Critical Metals (ASX: MTM) for exclusive collaboration on refining Meteoric’s Mixed Rare Earth Carbonate (MREC) using Flash Joule Heating (FJH) technology.
  • FJH test results show significant MREC upgrade:
  • Magnetic rare earth oxide (MREO) content increased from ~30% to 72% of TREO.
  • High recovery rates for key magnetic elements:
    • Pr (76%), Nd (65%), Dy (75%), Tb (81%), Gd (89%).
  • Removal of low-value elements: 83% La, 88% Ce eliminated.
  • Exclusivity clause: MTM barred from similar Brazil-based ionic clay REE deals with third parties during the 12-month MOU term.

Next Steps

  • Pilot plant development (Poços de Caldas, Brazil) targeted for September 2025, potentially hosting FJH demo facility.
  • Further FJH optimization to improve recoveries and La/Ce rejection.

Commercial Implications

  • Potential to establish alternative Western supply chain for critical magnetic REEs (Pr, Nd, Dy, Tb).
  • Downstream integration could enhance product value and market flexibility.
